    "description": "Grow your career with Milton International Enterprises! We are hiring a Assistant Store Manager for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Milton International Enterprises:\nMilton International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Milton International Enterprises!",
